## IMPORTANT NOTE:
For correct operation you will need another resource pack:
Harry's lib. A link to it is present in the Version section
## The resource pack is designed to add bus models detailed using JavaScript

There is one bus in the resource pack: Yutong ZK6108HGH.

The following functions are implemented using javascript: 
- working display;
- rotating wheels;
- turning front wheels;
- roll of the bus when turning;
- rotating steering wheel;
- correct animation of doors;
- headlights that light up at night;
- brake lights;
- reverse lights;
- turn signals.
